OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on the new
OL,7,Fparents placed in temporary
OL,8,Faccommodation after being evacuated
OL,10,FThe parents of a three-week-old baby
OL,11,Fgirl who was born shortly after they
OL,12,Fwere forced to leave their flat in
OL,13,FPlymouth say they feel 'traumatised'
OL,14,Fand left in limbo.
OL,16,FGeorgia James and her partner Dave
OL,17,FJones were among dozens of tenants
OL,18,Ftold to leave Evolution Cove in
OL,19,FStonehouse last month after the
OL,20,Fbuilding was deemed 'at risk of
OL,21,Fcollapse'.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,FBaby Eden was born prematurely two
OL,7,Fdays later, which Georgia believes may
OL,8,Fhave been triggered by the stress of
OL,9,Fthe move.
OL,11,FThe owner of the building says the
OL,12,Fwellbeing of residents remains their
OL,13,Ftop priority.
OL,15,F'She was so distraught and sad'
OL,17,FDave told ITV West Country: "The house
OL,18,Fwas completely changed into a nursery,
OL,19,Fso it was perfect and it was where we
OL,20,Fwanted to be with the baby.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,F"So being told that we had to get out,
OL,7,FGeorgia was like 'Well I'm not
OL,8,Fleaving, we're not leaving the house.'
OL,10,F"Obviously we were forced out in the
OL,11,Fend. She was so distraught and so sad,
OL,12,Fshe didn't sleep that whole night.
OL,14,F"Her waters broke, the next day we
OL,15,Fwere in hospital and we didn't get out
OL,16,Funtil a week later and she had the
OL,17,Fbaby. We asked the midwives and they
OL,18,Fsaid it can be brought on by stress."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,FDave, Georgia and Eden are currently
OL,7,Fin an AirB&B property, like dozens of
OL,8,Fothers, who have been told it will be
OL,9,Fat least another five weeks until they
OL,10,Fcan return.
OL,12,F'We've been ripped away from a bubble'
OL,13,FDave added: "We still don't feel at
OL,14,Fhome, we haven't got all of our stuff
OL,15,Fthere, we've just got baby stuff, and
OL,16,Fwe're living in someone else's house.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,F"So it's kind of hard for us to have
OL,7,Four life back. We're still in limbo.
OL,8,FWhat should have been the best week of
OL,9,Four lives turned into probably one of
OL,10,Fthe worst weeks.
OL,12,F"We have some sad nights where we're
OL,13,Fsitting there and we wish we were back
OL,14,Fat our flat. We rented the flat
OL,15,Fknowing we were going to have a child
OL,16,Fand we wanted to have that child in
OL,17,Fthat flat.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,F"We've been ripped away from that
OL,7,Fbubble now and we're in somewhere we
OL,8,Fdon't know, we don't know the people
OL,9,Faround us and it's just a little bit
OL,10,Fsad really."
OL,12,FA spokesman for Grey GR, the
OL,13,Fbuilding's owner, said: "It would not
OL,14,Fbe appropriate to comment on
OL,15,Findividual residents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,F"We know how difficult this process
OL,7,Fhas been and that some residents have
OL,8,Furgent personal concerns, and we
OL,9,Fcontinue to work as closely as
OL,10,Fpossible with these residents to
OL,11,Fensure they are safe and their
OL,12,Fwellbeing prioritised."
OL,14,F'I didn't know where to go'JMeanwhile,
OL,15,FSusanna Triki and her pet cockatiel
OL,16,Fare also trying to adjust to their new
OL,17,Ftemporary home.
OL,26,@tD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,FOn the night of the evacuation,
OL,7,FSusanna says she felt panicked and
OL,8,Fconfused.J"It was very scary to be
OL,9,Fhonest," she said.
OL,11,F"I went out in my shorts with my
OL,12,Fneighbours, I said, 'What's going on?'
OL,14,F"It was like, 'Oh, pack some clothes
OL,15,Fup, and you need to leave the flat,
OL,16,Fwe're all leaving, they said the flat
OL,17,Fis going to collapse.'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,F"When I packed my clothes, I didn't
OL,7,Feven know what I was packing. I
OL,8,Fliterally put in things I didn't even
OL,9,Fneed. Where am I going to go? I
OL,10,Fliterally have nobody in Plymouth to
OL,11,Fgo to."
OL,13,F'My mental health is really down'
OL,14,FResidents were given just one hour's
OL,15,Fnotice to leave as cracks had been
OL,16,Ffound in structural support beams in
OL,17,Fthe building's car park.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,FThe damage was first spotted in
OL,7,FDecember last year, but the building's
OL,8,Fowners said new information prompted
OL,9,Fan urgent evacuation.
OL,11,FSusanna was placed in a hotel for ten
OL,12,Fdays - leaving her cockatiel behind -
OL,13,Fbefore they were reunited in a small
OL,14,Fbedsit.
OL,16,F"The bed is in the kitchen, I don't
OL,17,Fhave any wardrobes, I don't have a
OL,18,Fdressing table or anything, the hoover
OL,19,Fis broken," she said,
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,F"My mental health is really down. I
OL,7,Fphoned my manager at work and said I
OL,8,Fcan't go to work. Social anxiety is
OL,9,Ftaking over a bit.
OL,11,F"They have to do something about it
OL,12,Fand give us clear answers. Mentally
OL,13,Fit's bad, I don't know how they're
OL,14,Fgoing to make it up to us."
OL,16,FThe building's owner, Grey GR, said
OL,17,Fresidents are expected to return in
OL,18,Fmid-May.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776355854
OL,3,CMum who gave birth after evacuation of
OL,4,C'unsafe' flats still in temporary home
OL,6,FA spokesman said: 'We are aware of how
OL,7,Fdistressing this situation is and have
OL,8,Foffered multiple one-to-one sessions
OL,9,Fwith the property management team to
OL,10,Fanswer any concerns, while a
OL,11,Fdesignated telephone hotline and email
OL,12,Faddress remain open and active to
OL,13,Frespond to further queries.
OL,15,F"We know how difficult this process
OL,16,Fhas been and that some residents have
OL,17,Furgent personal concerns, and we
OL,18,Fcontinue to work as closely as
OL,19,Fpossible with these residents to
OL,20,Fensure they are safe and their
OL,21,Fwellbeing prioritised."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
